File: Officials have recommended that people should ensure that they wash their hands using soap for 20 seconds. JOHANNESBURG - As the coronavirus (COVID-19) continues to spread throughout the world, health officials say hand-washing can help you protect yourself. Officials have recommended that people should ensure that they wash their hands using soap for 20 seconds. READ: Vietnamese COVID-19 safety dance goes...viral If you have ever tried to wash your hands for 20 seconds, then you know that it can be a little boring and feels like a long time. To help pass time, app developer @neoncloth on Twitter has created a website which allows you to generate hand washing instructions accompanied by lyrics from your favourite song. Wash Your Lyrics includes infographics that shows what you are supposed to do for each step.